The paper deals with the problem of Visual Question Answering, which involves understanding and encoding multi-modal inputs, performing reasoning over them, and predicting answers. This problem is at the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories that this paper belongs to, ordered from most to least likely.
